  "1885380": {
    "name": "Code ZIN: Esper Arena",
    "steam_appid": 1885380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >代码ZIN：埃斯珀竞技场是一款动作、竞技场、第三人称射击游戏，具有动漫角色的美感。它的背景是NetSphere，一个通用的、沉浸式的虚拟世界，被数十亿人用来生活、学习、工作和发展。Esper Arena是终极的vSport，具有无尽的娱乐性，令人着迷，并且在技能表达上没有底线。被称为 &quot;世界人 &quot;的玩家被赋予了战斗模块，这些模块模拟了他们的武器和能力。在刺激肾上腺素的战斗中测试你的反应能力和策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成功则成为不朽，失败则被遗忘。这是你获得荣耀的机会</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>免责声明</strong>：请注意，您并非总能立即找到匹配对象。这一情况将在我们进入正式发布阶段后发生重大改变。请通过我们的Discord频道寻找匹配对象！本次抢先体验阶段旨在收集反馈并优化游戏，为正式发布做准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/8275b197447508bf4a8561a95ba9a6f7.poster.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/8275b197447508bf4a8561a95ba9a6f7.webm?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/8275b197447508bf4a8561a95ba9a6f7.mp4?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/0e73664ce354465277e86a8ede91c520.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在竞争性的PVP行动中，玩家团队在封闭的竞技场上互相对峙，目标取决于游戏模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的本质是速度和策略。玩家能够从众多选择中装备三种武器和一种能力，根据偏好和个人实力，精心打造自己的经验。此外，他们的机动性很强，因为他们的角色配备了闪避和推进技术，这些技术与所选择的设备相结合，形成了无尽的游戏风格和选择，以应对任何和所有情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/1b147b23d47a56ced79cf7d8adb50790.poster.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/1b147b23d47a56ced79cf7d8adb50790.webm?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/1b147b23d47a56ced79cf7d8adb50790.mp4?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/d15c1c1d819ae83b6fd06653da7aa61a.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* 竞争性的PVP游戏玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* 各种武器和武器皮肤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* 各种能力的继承和装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*各种角色化妆品和定制选项</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* 团队死亡竞赛模式以及更多即将推出的模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*为每个游戏模式专门设计的地图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/f2c207db225921073fb27133126af004.poster.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/f2c207db225921073fb27133126af004.webm?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/f2c207db225921073fb27133126af004.mp4?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/e870432620100f0a384ec0d6b8965508.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些游戏模式之一是TDM，每队最多可以有5名玩家参加。每场比赛由最多5轮组成，每轮时间限制为6分钟。在这6分钟的时间限制内，谁的杀敌数量达到20个，或者在6分钟的计时器结束后，谁的杀敌数量领先，谁就赢得这一轮。赢得3轮比赛的队伍赢得比赛。协调是这里的关键，这得到了战术产卵的支持，让玩家在产卵到他们选择的区域之前就能洞察到战场的情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/2ea10ca19007264aaa120f763df46386.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的一个组成部分是定制。目的是在可能的情况下支持个性化，在游戏中，在游戏角色和其他方面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这块画布上描绘你的个性，创造你自己的英雄，通过角色和服装的定制，以及个性化的装载，支持你的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在网络空间环境中，通过手工制作的地图，可以了解到未来和多种游戏模式的发展，每一步都是你自己在广播。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/ecd803623ca2d06b14baba746ce7e42e.poster.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/ecd803623ca2d06b14baba746ce7e42e.webm?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/ecd803623ca2d06b14baba746ce7e42e.mp4?t=1763977684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885380/extras/23a38bcbe9eba95c93012fdcc49008ec.avif?t=1763977684\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的这个'自我'正是NetSphere创建的原因。为了创造一个自给自足的人工智能，世界上所有智能的累积，Zenith智能网络，称为ZIN，在网球的用户不知道的情况下被培养出来。2053年，人类已经开始向虚拟空间过渡，下一步的进化即将到来；技术奇点，智能爆炸，真正的人工智能。</p>",
